Swallen, Contr. U.S. Natl. Herb. 29: 253. 1948. Type: Venezuela, between La Trampa and Casadero, State of Merida, 28 April 1944, J. A. Steyermark 56182 (lectotype, designated as holotype by Connor &amp; Edgar, Taxon 23: 600 (1974): US 00133441!).
</paragraph>
